{"tid":1728162,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"如何對抗蛇齋餅粽","createTime":"2019-11-16T18:00:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-17T05:48:40.000Z","uid":302638,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0650b35757d990b3320312ee75afac0a18589900","tid":1728162,"uid":302638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T18:00:31.000Z","msg":"開左幾次吹水台都好快沉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n睇下開喺創意台得唔得<br />\n大家非p牌可唔可以幫我推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n相信大家屋企都有廢老收左蛇齋餅粽去投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n老一輩覺得收左人嘅禮物就要幫返人，呢樣野我地改變唔倒<br />\n但係我地可以做嘅係利用佢地另一樣改變唔倒嘅野<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">貪念<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n我地只要同啲廢老解釋返奶共班狗派野嘅目的就係要贏選舉，而佢地輸左嘅話嚟緊幾年就會派更多野想贏返下次選舉，咁班貪心嘅廢老就會自動波唔投奶共狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁多位孝順嘅子孫唔係唔幫手呀嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n幫我推呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f6a48e44df080d3d24219ded2aaf8094a420e94","tid":1728162,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T18:01:09.000Z","msg":"政府打緊公關戰同輿論戰，口誅筆伐黎解散呢場運動，手足知唔知我地下一步要點做？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1728096\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1728096</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"49b4031efbfd4878b3dfee5cbb3842dda2dd29c8","tid":1728162,"uid":302638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T18:01:48.000Z","msg":"有無人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"470bb43614f7282050fb3dbfae4dc9c153df0b68","tid":1728162,"uid":302638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T18:03:24.000Z","msg":"聽日再開過 開到你地睇倒為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"566f1494f40d87ca8c70c